    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="original">
                <pb facs="http://lilielbe.org/media/letters/1932-03-09HellerHarthern.jpg"/>
                <div rend="head" style="letter">
                    <p>
                        <anchor type="commentRangeStart" n="1"/>
                        <add place="leftMargin" type="insertion" rend="pencil">
                            <persName key="thomsenTC">Thomsen</persName>
                        </add>
                        <anchor type="commentRangeEnd" n="1"/>
                        <note type="translator" source="kej" corresp="comment_1">Written in the top
                            left corner in another hand.</note>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div rend="body">
                    <p>
                       Aussig, den <date when="1932-09-03">09.03.32</date>
                    </p>

                    <p>Ich las eine Besprechung Ihres Buches „Fra Mann til Kvinde“ und würde es
                        gerne ins Deutsche übersetzen. Bitte schreiben sie mir, ob und zu welchen Bedingungen Sie mir das
                        Übersetzungsrecht überlassen wollen.</p>

                    <p>Hochachtungsvoll,</p>
                    <signed>
                        <persName key="hellerH">Herta Heller</persName>
                    </signed>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <div rend="head" style="letter">
                    <p>
                        <anchor type="commentRangeStart" n="1"/>
                        <add place="leftMargin" type="insertion" rend="pencil">
                            <persName key="thomsenTC">Thomsen</persName>
                        </add>
                        <anchor type="commentRangeEnd" n="1"/>
                        <note type="translator" source="kej" corresp="comment_1">Written in the top
                            left corner in another hand.</note>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div rend="body">
                    <p>
                        Aussig, den <date when="1932-09-03">09.03.32</date>
                    </p>
                    <p>I read a review of your book „Fra Mann til Kvinde“ and I would like to
                        translate it into German. Please let me know, if and under what conditions you would authorize this
                        translation.</p>

                    <p>Yours sincerely,</p>
                    <signed>
                        <persName key="hellerH">Herta Heller</persName>
                    </signed>

                    <!--note for transcriber: Harthern wrote 'Lili Elbe' in red across the bottom of letter-->

                </div>
            </div>
